      "post_content": "Why would you ever use this ability? The whole idead of unsummonong your own creatues is to stop them from dying, as it is the ability is basicallt useless. Lets not get started on the fact that its a 1/1 creature for 4 mana, without haste or flash.  \n  \nBetter idea:  \n2BB, flash 1/1  \nHaste, T: return (name) and target creature you control to their owner's hands.",
      "posted_by": "Kurraga",
